Data.title: Road Obstacle Detection
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: This program uses OpenCV and Tensorflow to detect potholes in Images, and Videos. The model was built using YOLOv5 and the pothole dataset from RoboFlow.com. Currently, this project is under development.

Data.title: Alpine - Yahoo & Alpha Vantage Stock Market Data
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: This program uses Yahoo and Alpha Vantage to collect and display stock details for the user. The program is currently under development.

Data.title: 3D Geotab Mapping
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: Application uses MAPBOX to display Geojson data. Interactive, thoroughly customizable maps in the browser, powered by vector tiles and WebGL.

Data.title: Halo Statistics API
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: The API officially used by Halo Waypoint, this service allows developers to return details about different players and their service records. This includes Win/Loss ratio, hours played, spartan armour used, and favorite game modes.

Data.title: Automobile Logo API
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: This Vehicle API provides access to a library of vehicle Logos. Instead of using an ID, Logos are retrieved using the Manufacturer Name.

Data.title: Osteoporosis Machine Learning Detection
Data.author: Ed Sykes, Ravi Jain, Alex Canales, Wei Bin Wang, Mohit Deol, Jennifer Weldon, Rohit Shanker, Volodymyr Voytenko, Jansen Sullivan, Doug Sauer
Data.metadata: Towards Better Insights: Preliminary Results Of A Machine Learning Model For Fracture Risk Assessment
Data.description: Create a Machine Learning (ML) model that predicts the BMD T-score and assesses the fracture risk based on relevant patient data features.

Data.title: Portfolio Website
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: Portfolio to showcase my projects. This includes Mobile Apps, Web Apps, Front-End projects, APIs, Data Science work, and Embedded systems development.

Data.title: Image Downloader
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: Program Downloads Images from the Internet and saves them to a local repository. Application makes use of Streamlit and Pytest. The image links are saved to a Postgres Database for further development.

Data.title: Image Downloader APIs
Data.author: Alex
Data.description: Multiple APIs built for development. Makes use of .NET Core for C# Development, NodeJS for Javascript, and Laravel for PHP. The image links are saved to a Postgres Database for further development.
